local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["endorphin"]={"endorphin","[en'dɔːfɪn]","[ɛn'dɔrfɪn]","n.内啡肽",'n.内啡肽','endorphin','内啡肽','The combination of a good guffaw and exercise is said to stretch muscles and trigger endorphins - the chemical in the brain known for its feel-good effect.','Any of a group of hormones secreted within the brain and nervous system and having a number of physiological functions. They are peptides that activate the body\'s opiate receptors, causing an analgesic effect'}
